U'Bay LUMUMBA, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Respondent-Respondent. C-449 September Term 2018
081784 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 18, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-003852-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
